title: I finally rode the weird, curved German elevator.
description:
At the New Town Hall, the Neues Rathaus, in Hanover, there's a strange elevator where the track curves unevenly. For years, people from Germany have been emailing me about it: well, I finally visited. ■ More about the Hall: https://www.visit-hannover.com/en/Sightseeing-City-Tours/Tourist-Highlights/The-New-Town-Hall

Camera: Maximilian Unger
Producer: Viktor Sramo at Klein Aber
